      "span_text": "On the basis of the location of the miRNA generation, miRNAs are grouped into two classes: (A) Intergenic miRNAs are generated from transcripts of miRNA genes located between protein-coding genes; (B) Intragenic miRNAs are generated from transcripts of sequences located within the protein-coding genes (Fig. 1)."
